OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FA woman who jumped out of a window
OL,7,Ffrom fear when Valdo Calocane kicked
OL,8,Fat her door could have been killed by
OL,9,Fhim, the Nottingham attacks public
OL,10,Finquiry has heard.
OL,12,FAn officer who visited the woman after
OL,13,Fshe was discharged from hospital with
OL,14,Finjuries to her spine told her she had
OL,15,Fbeen "brave" when she escaped and
OL,16,Fwarned Calocane could have killed her
OL,17,For been violent if he got to her, the
OL,18,Finquiry in central London was told.
OL,26,@wD@FOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/14
