PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FCalocane, who was 31 at the time of
OL,7,Fthe attacks, had already been arrested
OL,8,Fearlier that same day on suspicion of
OL,9,Fcausing criminal damage to a different
OL,10,Fdoor, but the incident was not given
OL,11,F"the attention it deserved" and police
OL,12,Fbody-worn camera footage of that
OL,13,Farrest cannot be found, chairwoman to
OL,14,Fthe inquiry Deborah Taylor heard on
OL,15,FThursday.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/14
