OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FThe former student killed University
OL,7,Fof Nottingham undergraduates Barnaby
OL,8,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,9,F19, and caretaker Ian Coates, 65, and
OL,10,Fattempted to kill three more people in
OL,11,Fthe early hours of June 13, 2023.
OL,13,FThe inquiry heard that more than three
OL,14,Fyears earlier, on May 24 2020, a young
OL,15,Fwoman thought there was a group of
OL,16,Fburglars trying to break in when the
OL,17,Ftriple-killer, who on another day
OL,18,Fthreatened to rape his neighbour's
OL,19,Fpartner, shook her door while she was
OL,20,Fin the shower.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,F"I thought that someone wanted to hurt
OL,7,Fme."
OL,9,FThe woman, who has not been named,
OL,10,Fgave evidence with the help of an
OL,11,Finterpreter and said she heard
OL,12,F"someone knocking repeatedly on the
OL,13,Fdoor", which "became louder and louder
OL,14,Fwith kicks".
OL,16,FWhen the woman asked who was there,
OL,17,FCalocane replied "it's me, open,
OL,18,Fopen", the inquiry heard.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@EO]uD@NOUvD@KO]yD@ROUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FShe said: "I could see that the door
OL,7,Fwas shaking, I could feel it coming
OL,8,Foff.
OL,10,F"I thought as a matter of fact it was
OL,11,Fa group of thieves or someone who
OL,12,Fwanted to hurt me."
OL,14,FShe said she leant out of the first-
OL,15,Ffloor window, which was 10-12ft from
OL,16,Fthe ground, and was "shouting for
OL,17,Fhelp", but no-one was around because
OL,18,Fof the Covid lockdown.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUtD@SO]xD@UOUyD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FThe woman continued: "I tried to jump
OL,7,Fbut I slipped and I fell on to the
OL,8,Fground. I was scared, I was very
OL,9,Fscared.
OL,11,F"I was shaking. I could not hold on to
OL,12,Fthe window very well at all. I thought
OL,13,Fthat someone wanted to hurt me, I did
OL,14,Fnot know what to do. I was by myself."
OL,16,FShe told the inquiry Calocane tried to
OL,17,Fcome to her again after she fell but
OL,18,Fpolice "pinned him down".
OL,20,F"I thought the psychiatric hospital
OL,21,Fwas not enough."
OL,26,@nD@VOUsD@AOUvD@fO]zD@HOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard the woman, who had
OL,7,Fnever seen Calocane before, underwent
OL,8,Fsurgery on her spine and is in
OL,9,F"constant" pain.
OL,11,FSpeaking about what an officer told
OL,12,Fher after the fall, the witness said:
OL,13,F"He also told me I had been brave, if
OL,14,FI had not jumped out of the window
OL,15,Fmany things could have happened to me.
OL,17,F"He could have killed me or could have
OL,18,Fbeen violent."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]uD@AOUyD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FShe added: "They (police) said they
OL,7,Ftried doing anything they could but
OL,8,Fbecause of his mental health problems,
OL,9,Fthey mentioned schizophrenia, this
OL,10,Fperson could not be jailed and he was
OL,11,Ftherefore taken to a mental health
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,14,F"I was very upset and angry. I thought
OL,15,Fthis was not enough, the psychiatric
OL,16,Fhospital was not enough, but because
OL,17,Fthere were no other possibilities I
OL,18,Faccepted it."
OL,26,@nD@LOUvD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FThe woman said: "I thought 'what would
OL,7,Fhappen to the person who tried to
OL,8,Fattack me ` how would this end?'"
OL,10,F"I don't know what happened to that
OL,11,Ffootage."
OL,13,FAsked whether the first incident
OL,14,Finvolving Calocane that day had been
OL,15,Fgiven the attention it deserved,
OL,16,FNottinghamshire Police inspector Katie
OL,17,FEustace said: "No, I don't think it
OL,18,Fwas."
OL,26,@nD@QOUpD@aO]yD@OOUzD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
