OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard that after his first
OL,7,Farrest that day, Calocane was talking
OL,8,Fabout seeing "devils and demons",
OL,9,Fbefore he was released back to the
OL,10,Fsame accommodation.
OL,12,FAfter the first incident, an officer
OL,13,Femailed the owners of the building
OL,14,Fasking if they wanted to "press
OL,15,Fcharges".
OL,26,@pD@NOUpD@`O]vD@ZOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FAsked whether there was a reluctance
OL,7,Fto pursue the incident as a criminal
OL,8,Fmatter, Ms Eustace said: "I would say
OL,9,Fit's not the best email," adding she
OL,10,Fwould have got a statement from the
OL,11,Fbuilding's owners.
OL,13,FMs Eustace said she alerted the
OL,14,Finquiry team that she could not find
OL,15,Fher body-worn camera footage of the
OL,16,Fincident with Calocane that occurred
OL,17,Fhours before the woman jumped out the
OL,18,Fwindow.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@YO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FShe said: "Unfortunately I don't know
OL,7,Fwhat happened to that footage, and
OL,8,Fit's incredibly frustrating for myself
OL,9,Fas a witness I couldn't use it to
OL,10,Frefresh my memory, or for the inquiry
OL,11,Fto be able to see it."
OL,13,F"He threatened to come back and rape
OL,14,Fthem."
OL,16,FOne of Calocane's neighbours at Brook
OL,17,FCourt in Nottingham, who was referred
OL,18,Fto as Liam, told the inquiry he
OL,19,Frecalls the killer knocking at his
OL,20,Fdoor on four or five occasions over an
OL,21,Funspecified period of time.
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@VO]vD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/14
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
