PN,37813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1772291020
OL,3,CValdo Calocane 'could have killed'
OL,4,Cwoman years before deadly attacks
OL,6,FSpeaking about one occasion in early
OL,7,F2022, the witness said: "The last time
OL,8,Fhe came to my door, he did threaten to
OL,9,Frape my partner."
OL,11,FThe witness said Calocane went down
OL,12,Fthe stairs, adding: "I followed to
OL,13,Fmake sure he left the building itself.
OL,14,FHe saw my partner leaning out the
OL,15,Fwindow. That's when he threatened to
OL,16,Fcome back and rape them."
OL,18,FThe witness said he did not call the
OL,19,Fpolice because he thought it would be
OL,20,Fa "waste of time".
OL,26,@oD@YOUqD@QO]tD@UOUxD@YO]|D@COU|D@QO]
